00:22:03.720 --> 00:22:06.480
any experience in the field.

00:22:06.480 --> 00:22:08.070
This is Stanislaus.

00:22:08.070 --> 00:22:11.670
Stanislaus was our guide
from the Chernobyl authority.

00:22:11.670 --> 00:22:13.860
He's been working at
the plant since 1991

00:22:13.860 --> 00:22:17.400
and is a fantastic
resource for information.

00:22:17.400 --> 00:22:20.240
This is Ed, who I believe
I talked about earlier.

00:22:20.240 --> 00:22:22.260
And this is Ryan Pierce.

